Ab agar maan lo jahan ki buylead aap dekh rahe ho wahan ho sakta hai allot kam ho rahi hai abhi dekhiye 43 minute pehle aayi hai ek Saharanpur ki 2000 piece 200 piece. Haan. Nahi 66 piece ki aayi hai 100 piece sorry sir. 100 piece sir. Aur ek clip ki aayi hai clone plant ki Dharampur se 400 plants ki.

Customer: Ji.

Executive: Uske neeche main dekh raha hu aayi hai green organic strawberry plant outdoor ki lead aa rahi hai sir. Par ab yahan pe dekhiye aapke jo paas lead ka option hai wahan pe do ghante pehle aayi thi mahaguni wali mahaguni wali band kar diye kar rahe hain?

Customer: Nahi kar raha hu lekin uska kam kar raha hu.

Executive: 100 piece 200 piece mein uthata nahi.

Executive: Uska minimum kitna piece uthata hai?

Customer: Itna to jitne ka maal na aaye itne ka to bhada aa jata hai.

Executive: 500 piece to utha lenge minimum?

Executive: Haan haan haan to dekhiye 500 piece aayi thi ab woh Chhattisgarh ki thi. Dur tha na. Hmm ye bahut dur tha. To isme bhi utna bhada aa jata jitna maal bhi na hota.

Executive: Dur rehne ka yahi dikkat hai ke agar bhai agar wahan ki na aaya to kya matlab ab dekhiye ek aayi hai ye to koi lag rahi hai recent lead mere khayal se jahan ki hai. Achcha ye order value aap laga ke nahi bhej rahe ho kya?

Customer: Matlab?

Executive: Order value ka option laga ke bheja kariye.

Customer: Order value ka?

Executive: Order value ka laga ke bhejege jaise 50000 ke upar ka order ab jaise maine kiya na abhi to do ghante pehle ek aapke paas aayi thi care leaf plant capri disora care plant keh raha hai aise kuch karke diya hai hazar plant chahiye.

Customer: Garden plant hi hai ye.

Executive: Are nahi karta hu.

Executive: Achcha achcha. Ab isme dekha 10000 ka laga ke order value to to bhi isme kai lead dikh jati hai. Yahan se lead lead ka aap woh laga order value ke hisab se to thoda sa aapko mil jayegi aur catalog views jo aaya tha woh us par baat hui sir eclipse clone plant ka tha.

Customer: Haan catalog views to main sabse karta.

Executive: 18 ghante pehle aayi thi aapne check bhi nahi kiya.

Customer: Kaun si?

Executive: Uh eclipse clone plant.

Customer: 18 ghante pehle yesterday kal?

Executive: Haan kal aayi thi.

Customer: Buylead mein?

Executive: Buylead mein haan.

Customer: Isme aa gaya. Buylead mein. Popular plant ka growth zyada chal raha hai is time popular. Popular ki booking nahi ho rahi hai.

Executive: Popular ki booking nahi ho rahi hai.

Executive: Sir yahi hai na main ek option bata raha hu aapko jab bhi laptop mein baithenge na to wahan pe jo aapko maine bataya tha ki uh call kar lijiyega kya auto refresher yaad hai?

Customer: Ji.

Executive: Auto refresher dal lenge to aapko lead aur achi tarah se dikhne lagegi lead hai sir bas yahi hai ki aap 10 12 chahte hain to do char aa rahi hai bas isi ka woh hai thoda kam hai.

Customer: Ji.

Executive: To fir woh aane lagegi aisi koi baat nahi.

Executive: Theek hai?

Customer: Okay okay.

Executive: Uh ab ye keh raha tha jo function open hua tha sir isko main close kar de raha hu haan tabhi bhi koi issue rahe to mujhe direct call kar lijiyega mera number save hai aapke paas?

Customer: Ji haan.

Executive: To mere paas direct call kariye na. Laptop mein open kiya tha kal laptop chala liya tha na main. Achcha achcha chala liya ye bahut achi baat hai.

Executive: Achchi baat hai aap laptop pe rehte hain active. Ha main ye ticket close kar de raha hu sir aapke paas ek feedback jayega jaise gaya tha pichli baar to woh yes kar dijiyega please. Koi bhi zarurat rahe aap turant mujhe phone kariye theek hai. Okay. Ki aapki lead nahi aa rahi hai lead dekho ya fir lead bhejne ki hui kuch bhi aap mujhe turant whatsapp pe message karo main turant aapko react karunga. Theek hai? Okay. Theek hai. Thank you aur koi issue to nahi hai na sir?

Customer: Aur koi issue nahi hai.

Executive: Theek theek. Okay. Thank you.

- Advised to use order value filter for leads.

- Informed about available leads in buyleads.

- Ticket will be closed, feedback will be sent.



Next Steps: 

- Customer to provide feedback on the ticket.

- Executive to be contacted for any further assistance.
